prodNameE: TYSONBIO SUPERB Blood Glucose Monitoring System
ingredientsDesc:
1. Each blood glucose test strip contains:
  (1) 1.4% w/w glucose oxidase
  (2) 2.6% w/w potassium ferricyanide
  (3) 96% w/w non-reactive ingredients
2. Each bottle (1.5ml) of control solution contains:
  Low: 0.03% w/v glucose, 0.2% dye, 99.77% non-reactive ingredients
  Normal: 0.06% w/v glucose, 0.2% dye, 99.74% non-reactive ingredients
  High: 0.20% w/v glucose, 0.2% dye, 99.6% non-reactive ingredients
